title: Lowry scores 40 points to lift Raptors to 112-105 win
text:
Lowry scores 40 points to lift Raptors to 112-105 win Associated Press | 0 comments 
TORONTO (AP) — Kyle Lowry scored 40 points to help the Toronto Raptors beat the Minnesota Timberwolves 112-105 on Monday night.
